  "url": "https://www.lankadeepa.lk/latest_news/\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda-\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0da7-\u0d9c\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2-\u0dad\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dd6-\u0dc3\u0da2\u0db6-\u0dc3\u0d82\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db0\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a\u0d9c\u0dda-\u0db4\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dcf-\u0dbb\u0da7-\u0db4\u0db1\u0dd3-/1-616554",
  "time_ut": 1658056868,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda \u0d9c\u0dd9\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2 \u0dad\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dd6 \u0dc3\u0da2\u0db6 \u0dc3\u0d82\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db0\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a\u0d9c\u0dda \u0db4\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dcf \u0dbb\u0da7 \u0db4\u0db1\u0dd3?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Ranil's house was set on fire by the son of a Sahaba organizer.",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Criminal investigation department sources say that a son of a former deputy minister who was wanted for arrest after setting fire to the private house of Acting President Ranil Wickramasinghe last night has fled the country.",
        "Sources of the Criminal Investigation Department say that the son of this Deputy Minister has left for Dubai last night (10).",
        "According to the report, the father of the fugitive suspect is a deputy minister in the Mahinda Rajapaksa government, and later he left the party and joined the Samagi Jana Balawega, and currently he is working as a constituency organizer in an area near Colombo.",
        "After occupying the President's House for the last (9) days, the activists went to the house of Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe, the politician's son, and released a video on social media saying, \"We are going to raid Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe's house just as we raided the President's House, and to inform the people who value the country to come for it.\" Ranil Wickramasinghe's house was raided and he requested through the video not to leave the house until he received the letter of resignation from the post of Prime Minister.",
        "Police sources say that investigations have been started regarding a woman who recorded this video from there, and the woman has been in contact with a politician who was engaged in struggles in many areas including Colombo and engaged in struggles with her on several occasions.",
        "According to sources of the Criminal Investigation Department, the Criminal Investigation Department has taken over all the videos and photographs related to these incidents and started investigations."
      ],
